    <p>Tree are displayed in the arborescence depending on its tags.</p>
    <p>To make a tree appear in the IT categorie, add the "IT" tag; to appear in the categorie IT, subcategorie Programming, add both "IT" and "Programming" tags (only adding "Programming" won't do).
    </p>
